                <p>
                    This site itself is one of my projects, built with Blazor WebAssembly and deployed on Azure using GitHub-based CI/CD. It features a clean, responsive UI with subtle animations designed to be fast, responsive, and visually engaging. It showcases a modern component-based design and responsive layout principles.
                </p>
                <div class="project-links">
                    <a href="https://github.com/DavPadDev/DavPadDev.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                        View Code on GitHub →
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="project-card">
                <h3>Project Two</h3>
                <p>
                    Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Curabitur vel sapien ut risus luctus volutpat. Aenean suscipit eros et enim euismod, quis hendrerit nibh tincidunt.
                </p>
                <a href="/projects">View Project →</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="projects-link">
            <a class="btn" href="/projects">See All Projects</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Call-to-Action -->
    <section class="cta fade-in delay-3">
        <h2>Let’s Work Together</h2>
        <p>Interested in collaborating or learning more?</p>
        <div class="cta-buttons">
            <a class="btn" href="/resume">View Resume</a>
            <a class="btn secondary" href="/contact">Contact Me</a>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>
